        <updateDate>2005-10-04T15:40:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) increase from 50 to 100 percent the cost percentage of qualified refinery property eligible for expensing; and (2) extend until January 1, 2015, the placed-in-service requirement for such property.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
